### GET all doctors filtered by specialization
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Doctors?$filter=specialization eq 'Cardiologist'

### GET appointments for a specific date
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments?$filter=appointmentDate eq 2025-07-01

### POST a new patient
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "ID": "PAT006",
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Walker",
  "dateOfBirth": "2000-01-01",
  "gender": "Male",
  "bloodGroup": "A_POS",
  "phone": "9876511116",
  "email": "john@gmail.com",
  "address": "California",
  "emergencyContact": "9876512227",
  "registrationDate": "2025-07-10"
}

### POST a new appointment
POST http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments
Content-Type: application/json
 
{
  "ID": "APP009",
  "appointmentDate": "2025-07-10",
  "appointmentTime": "10:00:00",
  "status": "Scheduled",
  "reason": "General Checkup",
  "notes": "Regular Visit",
  "fee": 1200
}

### GET patients filtered by blood group
GET http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Patients?$filter=bloodGroup eq 'O_POS'

### PATCH appointment status to Completed
PATCH http://localhost:4004/odata/v4/hospital/Appointments('APP001')
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "Completed"
}
